import React from 'react' import classes from './InsideHotel.module.css' const InsideHotel = args => { //console.log(args.location.state.imageurl) return(
{args.name}
{args.rating}
< i class="fa fa-money" aria-hidden="true" style={{fontSize:"111.3%"}}> {args.price}
) } export default InsideHotel;
